        "  * What the DICOM standard is\n",
        "  * How computers represent scan data\n",
        "  * What data is in a DICOM file\n",
        "* Workshop content will include:\n",
        "  * Opening and rendering DICOM with Python\n",
        "  * Extracting demographics from DICOM\n",
        "\n",
